      "text": "（スリクスは元BIG4で、実力も十分）\n（舞台さえ整えれば、すぐトップに返り咲けるはず）",
      "startTime": 129.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_02-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "何よ、人の顔じろじろ見て",
      "startTime": 133.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_01_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（……はずなんだけど）\n（それも、やる気があれば、の話なんだよな……）",
      "startTime": 139.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4366.666666700013,
          "startTime": 144.0666666667
